OL,5, "The social contract" between parents  
OL,6, and schools has become fractured, the  
OL,7, head of Ofsted has said.               
OL,9,FIn her final annual report, Amanda     
OL,10,FSpielman says the "unwritten agreement"
OL,11,Fensuring families take their children  
OL,12,Fto school and respect the policies, in 
OL,13,Freturn for a good education, "will take
OL,14,Ftime to restore".                      
OL,16,FParents are increasingly willing to    
OL,17,Fchallenge school rules, she says.      
OL,19,FMs Spielman is stepping down at the end
OL,20,Fof the year.                           
